cu.explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_PUSCH to 0 will cause invalid thread allocation and prevent PUSCH processing.
cu.explanation_zh: 將 Num_Threads_PUSCH 設定為 0 會導致無效的線程分配，並阻止 PUSCH 處理。

du.explanation_en: Setting absoluteFrequencySSB to an out-of-range value will cause SSB frequency misalignment and prevent SSB transmission.
du.explanation_zh: 將 absoluteFrequencySSB 設定為超出範圍的值會導致 SSB 頻率錯位，並阻止 SSB 傳輸。
